  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 3</strong> Abjuration</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 120 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nChoose one creature, object, or magical effect within range. Any ongoing spell of level 3 or lower on the target ends. For each ongoing spell of level 4 or higher on the target, make an ability check using your spellcasting ability (DC 10 plus that spell's level). On a successful check, the spell ends.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> You automatically end a spell on the target if the spell's level is equal to or less than the level of the spell slot you use.</p>",
